caption.p: Phylogenetic analysis of the phlebovirus amino acid sequence. Neighbor-joining (NJ) phylogeny trees were generated using the Kimura 2-parameter model with 1000 bootstrap replication. ( A) L protein amino acid sequence (167 AA). ( B) Gc protein amino acid sequence (170 AA). ( C) Nucleoprotein amino acid sequence (170 AA).
